    public abstract class TDetailFieldBaseDecorator<M extends TModelView>
extends TDynaViewSimpleBaseDecorator<M>
    The basic decorator of the table detail view. It can be applied on detail entities. A TableView is created to list the details.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
